name: Clerkship/Clinical Rotations (via LWW Heatlh Library) (Wolters Kluwer)
description: Provides core texts needed for each of the core clerkship rotations highly recognized titles and clerkship-specific series for Internal Medicine, OB/GYN, Pediatrics, Surgery, Family Medicine, and Psychiatry. Also available access to Key series titles Step-up, Recall, Blueprints, Shelf Life, and BRS.
